        "content": "<p>Yeah, I didn't think too carefully about naming and there are certainly several places where it would better to align with Mathlib style.  I suppose <code>add_of_LIM</code> could be <code>LIM_add_distrib</code> instead, and <code>sub_of_cauchy</code> maybe should be <code>Sequence.isCauchy.sub</code> instead?  I guess one could find the closest Mathlib counterpart to these results as a naming guide.</p>",
